title: Use ACTION_GET_CONTENT intent when selecting files
message:
Use ACTION_GET_CONTENT intent when selecting files

This intent is recommended over the ACTION_OPEN_DOCUMENT intent for
cases where the file is not intended to be opened for a prolonged period
of time.
